I promise you.

334
00:23:08,600 --> 00:23:11,750
♫And take the risk♫

335
00:23:09,690 --> 00:23:10,900
Mr. Yan.

336
00:23:10,920 --> 00:23:12,380
You have to promise me that

337
00:23:12,510 --> 00:23:14,240
