502
00:31:58,320 --> 00:31:58,990
So,

503
00:31:59,400 --> 00:32:02,000
come to my house for dinner this weekend, okay?

504
00:32:05,220 --> 00:32:06,350
I'll prepare for it.

505
00:32:07,450 --> 00:32:08,720
I'm leaving.

506
00:32:19,570 --> 00:32:20,100
Manning.

507
00:32:30,120 --> 00:32:32,040
I want to ask you something.

508
00:32:36,260 --> 00:32:36,990
Back then...

509
00:32:42,640 --> 00:32:43,300
That man...

510
00:32:43,730 --> 00:32:45,940
He was the thief who came to my house last time.

511
00:32:45,940 --> 00:32:47,400
He is holding my backpack.

512
00:32:49,040 --> 00:32:49,970
Wait for me here.

513
00:32:51,910 --> 00:32:52,770
Yan Xingcheng.

514
00:33:34,250 --> 00:33:34,940
What's wrong?

515
00:33:34,940 --> 00:33:35,800
What happened?

516
00:33:36,160 --> 00:33:37,680
I'm going to go after Xingcheng.

517
00:33:37,680 --> 00:33:38,600
Can you help me?

518
00:33:43,550 --> 00:33:44,100
Get in.

519
00:35:52,950 --> 00:35:53,720
Xingcheng.

